Zhang Ruochen gradually found that Lin Fei really care about him, simply meticulous, see Zhang Ruochen nightmare was scared to wake up, but regardless of the cold, immediately came to Zhang Ruochen's room.



In his last life, Zhang ruochen never met his birth mother. It is said that she died when she was born! Unexpectedly, after being killed by princess Chiyao, reborn in this body inside, actually let him more than a mother, feel the warmth of maternal love.
